The VI peripheral of Tegra supports capturing from MIPI CSI-2 or parallel
video (called VIP in the docs). MIPI CSI-2 is already implemented. Add a
VIP implementation.

Signed-off-by: Luca Ceresoli <luca.ceresoli@bootlin.com>
